<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GALAXY BATTLESHIP - Official</title>
    <style>
        /* 基本スタイル */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* 銀河と戦艦の背景 */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            background: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)),
                url('https://unsplash.com'); /* 銀河の画像 */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* 戦艦のシルエット（擬似要素で重ねる） */
        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10%;
            right: 5%;
            width: 80%;
            height: 40%;
            background: url('https://pixabay.com') no-repeat center/contain;
            opacity: 0.6;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px #00f2ff);
            pointer-events: none;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-1deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(1deg); }
        }

        /* コンテンツ */
        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #777);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(0,242,255,0.5));
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #00f2ff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* ボタン */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border: 1px solid #00f2ff;
            color: #00f2ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            background: rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.1);
            clip-path: polygon(10% 0, 100% 0, 90% 100%, 0 100%);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #00f2ff;
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00f2ff;
        }

        /* スマホ対応 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 0.2rem; }
            .subtitle { font-size: 0.9rem; }
            .hero::after { width: 100%; bottom: 5%; }
        }

        /* 装飾的なグリッド */
        .grid-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                              linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="subtitle">Deep Space Exploration</p>
            <h1>ARK-7 NEBULA</h1>
            <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 30px; line-height: 1.6; color: #ccc;">
                銀河の彼方へ。人類の新たな境界線を切り拓く、次世代宇宙戦艦「アーク7」の全貌がここに。
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Launch System</a>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
